name: Kumodot Follow Card #01
description: Buy that Card to add me your your collection. That's my idea of saving artists links to our collections and share them to the world as an "Artist Card". The QRCode bring to my hic et nunc URL. Works as a collectable too, or a way to show support to an artists, or save for visiting later and keep checking how he's evolving. Do your own card and Mint on your collection for free, so other artists can collect it too. Spread the idea, do it your own style if you feel so.
